reviewText: Obviously not modern cinema pieces, this collection is not a great sell for eroticism at all.  Many seemingly imagined and/or confusing sequences.  Not entertaining at all I'm afraid and raised more questions than it answered.  As for the Swedish goddess, there is no denying she was a stunning young model of the time but the dialogue given to her was unbelievable in more than one sense of the word.

Broken into three stories, first up is a group of psych PHDs talking about sex, and giving pretty good information if you are 12.  the others are pretty dated (70s), but if you are a fan of Stellan Skarsgard like I am, you will be thrilled to see Stellan in his early 20s!!
Louise

Christina Lindberg, the woman remained in my memory even after being out of High School for 30 years.
I first became acquainted with Ms Lindberg, back in 1968, i was on 42nd St., the way it was with all the ADULT Movie Theatre's, one of
the theatre's was showing INGA, just one look at the face and figure of Ms Lindberg, and i was smitten.
